# dnacenter_wireless_settings_rf_profiles (Data Source)

It performs read operation on Wireless.

- This data source allows the user to get all RF Profiles

- This data source allows the user to get a RF Profile by RF Profile ID

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "dnacenter_wireless_settings_rf_profiles" "example" {
  provider = dnacenter
  limit    = 1
  offset   = 1
}

output "dnacenter_wireless_settings_rf_profiles_example" {
  value = data.dnacenter_wireless_settings_rf_profiles.example.items
}

data "dnacenter_wireless_settings_rf_profiles" "example" {
  provider = dnacenter
  id       = "string"
}

output "dnacenter_wireless_settings_rf_profiles_example" {
  value = data.dnacenter_wireless_settings_rf_profiles.example.item
}
```
